	<b><span style=\"font-family:\'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';\">二&nbsp; 投资总额奖励<span></span></span></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-family:\'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';\">活动期间，投资总额<span>10</span>万以上奖励<span>100</span>元， <span>30</span>万以上奖励<span>600</span>元，<span>50</span>万以上奖励<span>1500</span>元<span></span></span></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<b><span style=\"background:white;color:red;font-family:\'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';\">注：<span>1 </span>投资总额按照投资月标的基数计算，比如<span>5</span>万投资<span>1</span>月标，投资总额为<span>5</span>万元；<span>5</span>万投资<span>2</span>月标，投资总额为<span>10</span>（<span>5*2</span>）万元；<span>5</span>万投资<span>3</span>月标，投资总额为<span>15</span>（<span>5*3</span>）万元；<span></span></span></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21pt;\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"background:white;color:red;font-family:\'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';\">2 </span></b><b><span style=\"background:white;color:red;font-family:\'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';\">投资总额奖励，统一在活动结束（即<span>3</span>月<span>8</span>日）后三个工作日内统一发放。</span></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21pt;\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"background:white;color:red;font-family:\'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';\"></span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:\'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';\"></span></b>&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-family:\'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';\">三&nbsp; </span></b><b><span style=\"background:white;color:black;font-family:\'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';\">注册即送<span>VIP</span>一年，<span>100%</span>本金保障<span>.</span>（<span>VIP</span>年费<span>150</span>元<span>/</span>年，<span>VIP</span>客户享受投资本金全额保障，抵押标享受全部投资本金和利息保障，非<span>VIP</span>客户只能享受<span>50%</span>的本金保障。）</span></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<b><span style=\"background:white;color:black;font-family:\'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';\"><span></span></span></b>&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"background:white;\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;background:white;color:black;font-family:\'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';\">四&nbsp; 活动期间，推荐有礼，每推荐一位好友成功投资月标<span>2</span>万以上的，奖励<span>50</span>元，若该好友成功投资月标<span>5</span>万以上的，则奖励<span>150</span>元。</span></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"background:white;\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;background:white;color:black;font-family:\'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';\"><span></span></span></b>&nbsp;<b><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:red;font-family:\'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';\">注：推荐好友奖励，在活动结束（即<span>3</span>月<span>8</span>日）后三个工作日内统一发放。请注意，推荐好友时一定告知好友写上介绍人的用户名；</span></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"background:white;\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:red;font-family:\'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';\"></span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;color:#444444;font-family:\'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';\"></span></b>&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-family:\'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';\">五&nbsp; 商富贷盖楼抽奖活动<span></span></span></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-family:\'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';\"><span>&nbsp;</span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:\'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';\">商富贷会不定期的举行盖楼抽奖活动，具体请详见公告；</span></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-family:\'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';\"><span></span></span></b>&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-family:\'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';\">本活动具体解释权归商富贷公司所有。</span></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-family:\'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';\"><span></span></span></b>&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-family:\'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:\'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';\">商富贷运营中心</span></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-family:\'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';\"><span></span></span></b>&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:236.25pt;\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-family:\'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';\">2013</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:\'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';\">年<span>2</span>月<span>20</span>日<span></span></span></b> \r\n</p>', '10', '0', '0', null, '1', '1361339389', '60.177.246.110');
